title: Aingels Cafe Bistro
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Bakery, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local cafe offering a couple of vegan options on the menu which change regularly. Other dishes can be veganized when you ask the owner. Stocks plant milk for drinks and sometimes a vegan cake. Shabby chic decor. Large car park is  adjacent to the cafe.
